    <td align="center">Unlabelled PNG image<br />(no gamma info)</td>
    <td><font size="1">&nbsp;</font></td>
    <td align="center">PNG image with gamma 1/1.6<br />(i.e. 0.625)</td>
    <td><font size="1">&nbsp;</font></td>
